{
  "stem": "9168.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't even teach it anymore, and we haven't for years-- maybe 35 or 40 years-- 30 years certainly, at least, at that time-- right about.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I was in high school from 1938 to 1942.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very minimal.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, the only paper we had was the in this little town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my life was so difficult working to bring in money from that hospital job for-- to supplement my mother's income, and my-- my brother-- my younger brother and sister in school.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it just seemed, you know, that that was all that I knew-- all that we knew-- in-- in those days, in that high school.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "High school activities-- I was involved in the artwork in-- which was an interest of mine, and worked on the school newspaper those years, and also a little bit of drama, and in the plays that the school put out.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But out-- in the outside world was non-existent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Within that community, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was an interesting little town built on a square-- and still is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And with-- that square is on the National Historic register.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was one Jewish family, the Wien family, W-I-E-N, who had a beautiful ladies' clothing store; gorgeous daughter who went to high school with us; and one black family.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Woodstock? 6,000.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 6,000-- 1 Jewish family, and 1 black family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one black family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We also had a-- a prominent Italian family, the Stompanado family, who had the beauty shop and the men's barber shop-- the only one in town.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was from that family, John Stompanado, a son, who became a member of the mafia, who killed-- let me see-- Lana Turner's-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] no-- Cheryl-- the daughter-- Lana Turner's boyfriend, I guess, in the bedroom.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
